Title: Bakery continues to build agents when one fails
Level: 1
Component: agents
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
Version: 1.5.0i1
Date: 1493966426
Class: fix

In case an error occured while baking new agents with the bakery
all not yet built packages were left unbuilt. This has been changed
now. All error are collected during building and written to the
user once all agents are done.
